text: Janel Brandtjen is an American businesswoman and politician who serves as a member of the Wisconsin State Assembly. == Early life and education == Born in Milwaukee, Wisconsin, Brandjten received a Bachelor of Business Administration in Finance and Marketing from University of Wisconsin–Milwaukee. == Career == Brandtjen is the owner of an advertising agency. She also served on the Waukesha County Board of Supervisors. On November 4, 2014, Brandtjen was elected to the Wisconsin State Assembly.Current Election Results == Personal life == Brandtjen is married and has two children. ==Notes== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:People from Menomonee Falls, Wisconsin Category:University of Wisconsin–Milwaukee alumni Category:Businesspeople from Wisconsin Category:Wisconsin Republicans Category:Women state legislators in Wisconsin Category:County supervisors in Wisconsin Category:Members of the Wisconsin State Assembly Category:21st- century American politicians Category:21st-century American women politicians
